  "text": "can also become important. 4 For example, including QED processes in the parton evolution will break the isospin symmetry as the up and down quarks have different couplings to the photon. xFitter is able to include NLO QED effects, and this is illustrated in Fig. 6 which displays the photon PDF as determined using a NNLO QCD and NLO QED analysis [CITATION_1] .",
