  "bib_entries": {
    "125304653": {
      "title": "The photon PDF from high-mass Drell Yan data at the LHC",
      "abstract": "In this contribution, we review the results of the recent paper \"The photon PDF from high-mass Drell Yan data at the LHC\" (arXiv:1701.08553), where a determination of the photon PDF from fits to recent ATLAS measurements of high-mass Drell-Yan dilepton production at centre-of-mass energy of 8 TeV is presented."
